node.text: THE PULSITOS FAM! 💘 So grateful for meeting such genuine, warm, HUNGRY humans in Sean + Laura - creators of @pulsitos_uk. Mad inspired by how you work + the drive you have- Bonnie + I (and Del who dipped before our shoot began🤣) has the most fun tonight. Thank you so much for having our goofy selfs! @_joviality love the friend I have found in you. 🔌 friendly reminder to all of you : YOU BECOME WHO YOU HANG OUT WITH. 🔌
Such a great wee night!!! Thank you for having us @pulsitos_uk  @natashaminter you're one amazing human being. 💚💚
